        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9781400034376" href="/book/show/9135306-the-invisible-bridge">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Rebecca by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/2355738-andrea-borod">Andrea Borod</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5875398-rebecca?shelf=historical-fiction">historical-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5875398-rebecca?shelf=holocaust">holocaust</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/5875398-rebecca?shelf=door-stoppers">door-stoppers</a>, 
